120
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:27,810
Nakarating ka na ba sa Hawaii? Mayroong apat na pangunahing isla sa Hawaii.

121
00:10:27,810 --> 00:10:30,550
Wow, grabe ka.

122
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,840
