Pero guys... I think you misunderstood the rumors.

126
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:51,870
Hindi ko alam kung kailan tayo magkakaroon nito.

127
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:54,210
Balita ko susunod na tagsibol.

128
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:57,410
Hindi, sinasabi ko na baka ito ang kaso

129
