talaga? Kanino?

192
00:15:15,830 --> 00:15:17,250
Buti naman—

193
00:15:17,250 --> 00:15:21,760
Guys! Ang pangyayaring ito ay hindi tumigil doon.

194
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:24,210
Nagdulot ito ng

195
